The '''Temple of Illumination''' was a [[temple]] on [[Chalacta/Legends|Chalacta]] and the headquarters of the [[Chalactan Adepts/Legends|Chalactan Adepts]]. [[Senator/Legends|Senator]] [[Yudrish Sedran/Legends|Yudrish Sedran]] consulted the Temple before deciding to oppose the [[Military Creation Act/Legends|Military Creation Act]].

